ications。","box":[[186,877],[901,878],[901,905],[186,904]]},{"text":"They alsoestablished awards","box":[[898,877],[1357,878],[1357,905],[898,904]]},{"text":"of l0-15 yuan for new technical designs or design improvements decided","box":[[186,909],[1327,910],[1327,938],[186,937]]},{"text":"by the bureau above。","box":[[186,943],[545,944],[545,968],[186,967]]},{"text":"It was a sheji jiangli, or a designing award。","box":[[544,944],[1316,944],[1316,971],[544,971]]},{"text":"They","box":[[1304,941],[1375,948],[1373,973],[1302,966]]},{"text":"have stressed business study--english, computers, etc。 during work hours,","box":[[182,971],[1374,977],[1374,1008],[182,1002]]},{"text":"and technical training courses.","box":[[184,1006],[696,1007],[696,1037],[184,1036]]},{"text":"They instituted awards for 'advanced technical workers' each year,","box":[[265,1036],[1341,1039],[1341,1073],[264,1069]]},{"text":"15 yuan, and 'quality model soldier', 15 yuan, about 6 persons for each","box":[[186,1072],[1342,1072],[1342,1102],[186,1102]]},{"text":"award.","box":[[186,1109],[288,1105],[289,1129],[187,1132]]},{"text":"This was in addition to the bonuses grades l-3。 Improvements in","box":[[312,1105],[1360,1106],[1360,1134],[312,1133]]},{"text":"work?","box":[[184,1142],[272,1139],[273,1163],[185,1166]]},{"text":"Things are more lax than during the CR in the offices。","box":[[295,1139],[1200,1140],[1200,1167],[295,1166]]},{"text":"Therewere","box":[[1210,1142],[1375,1145],[1374,1166],[1210,1163]]},{"text":"a lot of political pressures during the CR in offices,but now things are","box":[[185,1172],[1374,1173],[1374,1200],[185,1199]]},{"text":"relaxed，6","box":[[189,1209],[340,1209],[340,1230],[189,1230]]},{"text":"except when there is a rush job to be completed。1","box":[[328,1206],[1153,1206],[1153,1233],[328,1233]]},{"text":"Now they are","box":[[1143,1207],[1343,1209],[1342,1233],[1143,1231]]},{"text":"more","box":[[186,1243],[255,1240],[256,1261],[187,1264]]},{"text":"erelaxedthantheforcedmethodsof theCRwhentheyforcedpeopleto","box":[[243,1236],[1376,1239],[1376,1265],[243,1262]]},{"text":"work","box":[[184,1275],[255,1272],[256,1293],[185,1296]]},{"text":" overtime with pay all the time。","box":[[244,1270],[774,1270],[774,1297],[244,1297]]},{"text":"Office technical people have lots of opinions about the new policies。","box":[[268,1302],[1387,1303],[1387,1330],[267,1329]]},{"text":"Their bonuses are smaller than the workers and shop cadres,but they feel","box":[[186,1337],[1376,1337],[1376,1364],[186,1364]]},{"text":"that they make just as big a contribution。","box":[[187,1369],[870,1369],[870,1396],[187,1396]]},{"text":"They're also unhappy about","box":[[901,1368],[1327,1368],[1327,1398],[901,1398]]},{"text":"the lack of housing, it is still very tight。","box":[[186,1402],[938,1402],[938,1432],[186,1432]]},{"text":"The problem still hasn't","box":[[932,1403],[1325,1401],[1326,1428],[932,1430]]},{"text":"beensolved.","box":[[186,1438],[379,1438],[379,1458],[186,1458]]},{"text":"Of course the intellectuals are happy with the new policies of the","box":[[265,1467],[1343,1467],[1343,1497],[265,1497]]},{"text":"top levels to treat intellectuals better, as valuable。","box":[[185,1500],[1093,1499],[1093,1529],[185,1530]]},{"text":"But at thebasic","box":[[1096,1501],[1357,1501],[1357,1524],[1096,1524]]},{"text":"levels leading cadres of working class background are not entirely convinced,","box":[[185,1533],[1439,1532],[1439,1562],[185,1563]]},{"text":"and still have a prejudiced attitude (pianjian taidu) towards intellectuals.","box":[[185,1565],[1425,1564],[1425,1595],[185,1596]]},{"text":"An example of how this","box":[[184,1601],[549,1600],[549,1627],[184,1628]]},{"text":"comesout:","box":[[537,1604],[726,1604],[726,1624],[537,1624]]},{"text":"in promotion of leading cadresto union","box":[[757,1600],[1393,1600],[1393,1627],[757,1627]]},{"text":"head, youth league, party branch secretaries and vice secretaries, plant","box":[[182,1632],[1361,16